    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The engine and transmission are functional, but you should expect some minor mechanical quirks and typical wear on the interior and exterior. It has been maintained regularly to keep it roadworthy, but it is not a showroom piece. This is a practical choice for someone looking for dependable transportation at a reasonable price point.",
