    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for a daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few small stains, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, it has been regularly serviced and runs well, though buyers should expect the typical signs of use associated with a car of this age. It's a solid, honest car for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
